race.description: Maydan Livestock Transport Freestone Feedlot Handicap
race.comment: JENNI MOREESE (2) has been busting to win and finds the right race. She can position forward, and the middle distance should hold no fears. Three back he was narrowly beaten at Eagle Farm and that reads extra well. LET FLY (1) has been racing in stronger and go on his narrow defeat at the Gold Coast two-back when he led over 2200m in a 75. Has a low barrier and the 3kg claim brings her into it. WHATJEUDOIN' (9) maps for a soft run and is going well. Got back and just missed an unlikely win at Ipswich last time and he will be coming hard. UP AND COMER (7) is in a top stable and they've scratched the stablemate. Has disappointed from the pace his last two but will have taken benefit from the latest after the switch north. The blinkers come off and keep onside.
